{{define "subject"}}Your GradConnect account has been deleted{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi {{.FirstName}},

This confirms that your GradConnect account was just deleted.

Changed your mind? You have 30 days to recover everything. Just sign in normally at https://gradconnect.ng/login with your usual credentials, and your account will come back exactly as it was — bookmarks, applications, reviews, all of it.

After 30 days, your account and personal information are permanently removed and can't be restored.

If you didn't delete this account yourself, sign in immediately to restore it, then change your password at https://gradconnect.ng/forgot-password and contact us at support@gradconnect.ng.

Thanks for being part of GradConnect.

The GradConnect Team
{{end}}

